name: Employee Monthly OT
query:
SELECT date(`tabTimesheet`.`start_date`) AS "Date:Date:100",
      `tabTimesheet`.`employee` AS "Employee:Link/Employee:100",
      sum(`tabTimesheet`.`total_hours`) AS "Working Hours:Int:100"
FROM `tabTimesheet`
WHERE date(`tabTimesheet`.`start_date`) BETWEEN date('2018-05-01')
   AND date('2018-05-31')
GROUP BY `tabTimesheet`.`employee`
ORDER BY `tabTimesheet`.`start_date` ASC
